## சென்னைப் பல்கலைக்கழகத் தமிழ்ப் பேரகராதி
இதோபதேசம்
--
- itōpatēcam
- n. <</>hita+upa-dēša.
- 1. Friendly advice, salutary instruction;
- நற்போதனை.
- 2. A Tamil translation, by Nāganātha Panditar of Jaggna, of a Skt. work containing a popular collection of fables intermixed with didactic sentences and moral precepts, supposed to have been narrated by a BrAhman named ViSNusarman to some young princes,
- ஒரு நூல்.